headline: Charles Schwab Bank Ranks #1 in Customer Satisfaction Among Both Checking and Savings Providers in J.D. Power 2025 U.S. Direct Banking Satisfaction StudySM
summary: WESTLAKE, Texas, May 29, 2025--Charles Schwab Bank ranked #1 in customer satisfaction among checking providers in the J.D. Power 2025 U.S. Direct Banking Satisfaction Study.
